{"tid":194051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戒煙討論區","createTime":"2017-04-09T16:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T09:38:29.000Z","uid":68073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c338548a7a25ee4db05b29ffe50dbfd094eb0d30","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"而家戒左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前都戒過一陣 <br />\n頭幾日最辛苦 <br />\n跟住慢慢習慣左就會好番少少<br />\n希望今次可以提住自己點解戒煙唔好動搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇人戒緊/戒到煙？<br />\n有冇成功例子分享下<br />\n<br />\n另外祝其他努力改好緊自己既巴打成功<br />\n一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830249ac288a95fc222c69806e9465d876b10cf9","tid":194051,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n睇到個post就想食"},{"pid":"540b4fb79982c245debb00a10fb081e087dcd299","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母<br />\n睇到個post就想食</blockquote><br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e701d2902a2bab41af5ae17c1996d19deccbdac","tid":194051,"uid":85299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"我都想介 但係個同事日日請我食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9cd12da548b94aeac30c2d1d003b5936e90962","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612d8208084e96c1c0169332bad582f91b47d0c7","tid":194051,"uid":10730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"1個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c57131a128d5ca67da411725a0bcf5b62ec4c99","tid":194051,"uid":13581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"樓主有無考慮過用戒煙香口珠？<br />\n<br />\n每支煙大約有12mg尼古丁<br />\n<br />\n尼古丁無導致上癮<br />\n<br />\n所以由12mg到0mg其實好講意志<br />\n<br />\n亦會出現withdrawal syndrome<br />\n<br />\n例如食慾大增、心煩氣燥等症狀<br />\n<br />\n而每粒香口珠大約有2mg尼古丁<br />\n<br />\n當你煙癮起既時候拎黎替代食煙<br />\n<br />\n透過吸收低劑量尼古丁黎舒緩withdrawal syndrome既不適<br />\n<br />\n係個幾好既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51eff5bf57433c0f7fbb45156912a0dd99d2d05f","tid":194051,"uid":45032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"Hi夜媽媽訓唔到食翻支先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68652ff3e8bde0342ce87a5d1e5bb6811f46feb7","tid":194051,"uid":98940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:42:33.000Z","msg":"講左成年幾都戒唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  煙癮仲有心癮都戒唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de5070df21cc5bd30b69c3339562d3bd5801d89","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主有無考慮過用戒煙香口珠？<br />\n<br />\n每支煙大約有12mg尼古丁<br />\n<br />\n尼古丁無導致上癮<br />\n<br />\n所以由12mg到0mg其實好講意志<br />\n<br />\n亦會出現withdrawal syndrome<br />\n<br />\n例如食慾大增、心煩氣燥等症狀<br />\n<br />\n而每粒香口珠大約有2mg尼古丁<br />\n<br />\n當你煙癮起既時候拎黎替代食煙<br />\n<br />\n透過吸收低劑量尼古丁黎舒緩withdrawal syndrome既不適<br />\n<br />\n係個幾好既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想型啲咁戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前克服過withdrawl syndrome<br />\n食番係因為心癮同諗埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n就算而家都有啲辛苦 但仲頂得住<br />\n克服左依幾日就剩番心癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db827b966f486d000bde4cb3b7981f963463b1e3","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想介 但係個同事日日請我食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好耐以前話過戒 有個fd二話不說買左包新既比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但今次真係不了 經歷完失敗諗通左啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436f4c146b74443d4c2c4c3d83e09334493d5e6d","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勇士"},{"pid":"b341165d23edafee4a66cdc875ec5b2387cb7bf2","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講左成年幾都戒唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  煙癮仲有心癮都戒唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔夠決心？<br />\n我以前都係咁 <br />\n成日話戒好快就屌唔撚理食番枝先再算<br />\n不過決心同動力真係難搵啲<br />\n祝你搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bc8465de164d7a06d46a2e52456705cbf2fe5d","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:16:29.000Z","msg":"好唔開心 好煩 好撚想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a9828e634ef9904c949a0d8cda3cb819699f3b","tid":194051,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好唔開心 好煩 好撚想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經冇事lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855805c5f6f99ac333f71199d06eada29d566e72","tid":194051,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"戒你老母啊 食多d啊 想睇你早條仆街早d死 我就安樂"},{"pid":"562b380b2f2ce433205d363bc7e7cce4aaa20247","tid":194051,"uid":88166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好唔開心 好煩 好撚想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經冇事lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油呀巴打!<br />\n<br />\n好多時都係唔開心就想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實同人傾係最重要"}]}